{"tid":541091,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日本諧星元旦節目直播「裸藝」失敗！秒露GG全國觀眾看光","createTime":"2018-01-26T05:44:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T00:47:32.000Z","uid":9573,"like":48,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"e4fcfa14d7870ae9a63856b4a2ef16e7424c1b2c","tid":541091,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T05:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3076/d3076688.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3076%2Fd3076688.jpg&h=349cb54f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲AKIRA100%鐵盤遮下體的「裸藝」爆紅。<br />\n<br />\n日本諧星「AKIRA100%」（アキラ100%）展現裸藝爆紅！他脫光光僅用一個鐵盤遮下體，在眾人面前表演「翻盤子」，只要被看到露GG就算失敗，連觀眾也跟著緊張冒冷汗。他元旦在直播節目《第51屆爆笑Hit Parade 2018》表演時發生失誤，可能觸犯「公然猥褻罪」，引發各方議論，還傳出電視台要封殺，結果自己上傳「牛頓鐘擺」影片在網路超轟動！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3076/d3076687.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3076%2Fd3076687.jpg&h=edbca7e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲AKIRA100%鐵盤遮下體的「裸藝」爆紅。<br />\n<br />\nAKIRA100%在元旦節目中表演「雪茄盒」雜技，要騰空切換盒子排列，盒子上印著新年祝福討好彩頭，沒想到一秒之差，盒子漏接掉地上，等於在全國觀眾眼前露GG。他一度離開舞台，隨後又回來成功表演扳回一城，不過造成「放送事故」令電視台很不開心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3076/d3076695.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3076%2Fd3076695.jpg&h=b8e2b4dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼AKIRA100%表演「雪茄盒」失敗趴地。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3076/d3076686.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3076%2Fd3076686.jpg&h=2116a77d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n儘管失誤引發議論，AKIRA100%的知名度也火速攀升，25日在社群網站公開「牛頓鐘擺」的段子，鏡頭前放牛頓擺具，隨著鐵球晃動表演裸藝，且完美演出沒讓GG見光。他突然登上Yahoo熱搜榜冠軍，當時還不知道發生什麼事，原來是影片被網友分享，影片高達577萬人觀看，網友反應空前熱烈，失誤黑歷史瞬間被洗白啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3076/d3076686.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3076%2Fd3076686.jpg&h=2116a77d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲AKIRA100%表演「牛頓鐘擺」，網友分享超過577萬人觀看。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Dv0sHnolYyU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDv0sHnolYyU&d=6b8NNPeCEMRihft%2FqxBOAozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=cf88ca17\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Dv0sHnolYyU</a><br />\n▲AKIRA100%在元旦直播節目表演「雪茄盒」發生失誤。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0Y0y873dQcQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0Y0y873dQcQ&d=6b8NNPeCEMRihft%2FqxBOAozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=f3c33d4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0Y0y873dQcQ</a><br />\n▲AKIRA100%表演「牛頓鐘擺」大成功。"},{"pid":"89ac654c38adc179a46ffeb38e5a208967e0b171","tid":541091,"uid":75870,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T05:46:20.000Z","msg":"GG圖呢"},{"pid":"43f0b099de0cdd1c2bbc0b148db33354c9e11d3f","tid":541091,"uid":7854,"like":55,"dislike":11,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T05:50:10.000Z","msg":"擺明特登博上位者<br />\n<br />\n 痴塊布仔扮無著都得啦"},{"pid":"2cdb3976068290c27769bbfcd842188f8096a43e","tid":541091,"uid":53254,"like":141,"dislike":4,"score":137,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T05:55:29.000Z","msg":"點解會有人鍾意睇呢啲表演..."},{"pid":"c58c137994e55d910f5c1108cfa7104c767c8be4","tid":541091,"uid":15823,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T05:57:11.000Z","msg":"好似好短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e229f7e6d6883724afe018eeb5cb57f27fb04a65","tid":541091,"uid":65984,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T06:02:39.000Z","msg":"牙籤仔收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ddede0096b84dabbdbf7fd347dacf0044be99b3","tid":541091,"uid":44638,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T06:07:23.000Z","msg":"之前佢上LH挑戰左好多次 終於失手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06095f5b239320cbd7005b8a6ea20632b2f57859","tid":541091,"uid":164730,"like":56,"dislike